{"tid":841568,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=Slave】含片！「跟車男」手腳慢 遭司機拳頭侍候！","createTime":"2018-09-29T15:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T04:26:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"cecce01589fa86357370878c37daa31c5a9c8687","tid":841568,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180929/photo/bkn-20180929113428279-0929_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180929230342\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180929%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180929113428279-0929_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180929230342&h=367711b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片 :[click 入Link]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180929/bkn-20180929113428279-0929_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180929%2Fbkn-20180929113428279-0929_00822_001.html&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9VVeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=38fe0d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180929/bkn-20180929113428279-0929_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有智力問題的環保垃圾車「跟車男」，疑因工作手腳慢，長期遭「惡教練」用拳頭侍候。有讀者向東網報料，指一間由食物環境衞生署外判的環保垃圾收集公司，旗下一名負責馬鞍山及沙田屋苑的環保垃圾車司機，長期拳打腳踢一名同車的智障「跟車男」，包括拳擊、大腳踢及拍打頭部，受襲「跟車男」長年啞忍，有同事「睇唔過眼」，不忿司機無體恤同事的智力問題，拍片將事件公開。<br />\n<br />\n影片所見，「跟車男」近日在馬鞍山翠擁華庭收集垃圾時，疑未有將垃圾桶泊正在垃圾車後方，立即遭到同車司機大力拍打頭部，並嚴厲喝斥。該司機示範一次正確做法後，見「跟車男」又再犯錯，便再大力拍他頭部，在旁目擊一切的「站頭」未有開聲阻止，只是叉腰旁觀。<br />\n<br />\n報料的讀者表示，「跟車男」年約40多歲，有輕度智障，遭該名同車司機欺凌的情況已持續兩至三年。他指，「跟車男」工作能力正常，只是有時手腳較慢，即遭司機多處刁難及折磨，並認為對方有歧視成分，惟「跟車男」一路啞忍，從不敢還手。過去曾有同事向上司舉報，但事情仍持續發生，惟有偷偷拍低事發經過，更指「呢個打頭嘅影片只係冰山一角。」"},{"pid":"cbb6b91773381598a2610694f2e3c5166ff769e1","tid":841568,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180929/photo/bkn-20180929113428279-0929_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180929230342\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180929%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180929113428279-0929_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180929230342&h=6e69b89f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4c9c02bc097823a53764faabf5916fe55f8641a","tid":841568,"uid":19454,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/214850_088e5cbe5691f2e64c2a73a831246722.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F214850_088e5cbe5691f2e64c2a73a831246722.gif&h=8dae661d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69cb9ff233980cb0090099ce56f0e4eff2d91eed","tid":841568,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":44,"score":-42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:29:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62ee4ce8eb86a3e6efb56c8c92c70d9af44e9d18","tid":841568,"uid":57410,"like":5,"dislike":16,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:29:42.000Z","msg":"其實佢都好慘 有個弱智同事<br />\n<br />\n如果返緊工遇到「弱智」既同事真係想打柒佢"},{"pid":"c885ec77184813a27215626084e76e51845abe0e","tid":841568,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:32:08.000Z","msg":"對住2至3年都咁係會燥"},{"pid":"997cfec265c706894fbf7e1781e101f856112065","tid":841568,"uid":190540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:35:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fd9f15973490bb46dabd11f8e8235e9cc3b6f7f","tid":841568,"uid":190540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26c83d1a7b6f740ca19140f4c280f06120501477","tid":841568,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a23765254ce9915541237ac89609ce82df8ae9","tid":841568,"uid":205844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"69cb9ff233980cb0090099ce56f0e4eff2d91eed","tid":841568,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":44,"score":-42,"cit